text: Kare-ra (fushin-sha) wa, tenshi-tachi ga yattekite (kare-ra no tamashi o hikinuki),-nushi no (shobatsu no) meirei ga kudaru made matsu soto wa nai node wanai ka. Kare-ra izen ni moso no yona mono mo ita. Shikashi arra wa kare-ra o futo ni atsukatta wakede wanai. Daga kare-ra wa jibun jishin o (fushinjin ni yotte) gai shita dakedearu
